# This is my basic learning project i would like to develop it over time
# Borders function draw box on the edges of console made out of "#" signs
# LoadingLine function shows an animation of loading line out of  "#"
# LoadingPercentage function shows an animation of loading line and provide percentage of fullyfying whole console width
# LoadingCursor function shows an animation of spining stick kind of 
# UpDownAnimation function shows an animation of a "#" bouncing up and down
# ScreenBounceAnimation function shows an animation of a "#" bouncing of the boarders of console (like old windows logo on the edges of the screen)
# MoveUp function moves cursor up in the menu
# MoveDown function moves cursor down in the menu
